Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.20,0:01:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是分了七层\N由神仙居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒支配这座山的\N邪恶帝皇多恶达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.94,0:01:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一边在各界层\N与多恶达的魔神战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.51,0:01:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边以第七界层为目标进发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.84,0:01:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把直到第三界层的\N多恶达魔神打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.45,0:01:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令它恢复\N原来和平世界的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在身处第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把灼热之剑\N放回胡娜拉像之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个冰雪世界的第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.09,0:02:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能变回原来的温暖世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我要加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.13,0:02:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.54,0:02:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十话\N龙神丸在野野神殿飞散!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去\N我便没有立足之地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.58,0:02:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样也要打倒渡\N平息残兄弟的愤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.80,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样护着\N胡娜拉像便万无一失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要推啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.65,0:03:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忍耐啊\N渡,什么事也是忍耐第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!火美子,你坐定点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去怎么办啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生飞便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样比较暖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该快到野野神殿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.30,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,今次一定可以收拾你\N去吧!异形军团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸭子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.49,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,这里交给战神丸吧\N我要决上次的胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这里没有电话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.63,0:04:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电话啊\N线不是断了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是电话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,快点吧\N好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.54,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,在下说交给我办\N你还不明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.40,0:04:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下没有事会做不到\N也不会打不通电话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战-神-丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.48,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战神丸!立即赶来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在西蒙后面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了,战神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.48,0:05:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战神丸,大跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔,很有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师,后面啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!奇怪珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.56,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,是机会了\N野牛武一郎流,交叉字斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.60,0:06:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残兄弟大人,请饶恕我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.37,0:06:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!\N师傅很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河马万岁!河马万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是小儿科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残恶鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.22,0:06:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到我们魔界三兄弟\N展示实力的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.79,0:06:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残酷哥哥,这世上有人\N可以战胜我们三兄弟的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.73,0:06:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是为我们胜利的历史\N增加一个罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗?残豹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.63,0:06:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,又可以跟人说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.67,0:06:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是这样\N也可以给和我们同是四天王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.71,0:06:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在多恶达身边献殷勤的\N东哥罗一个下马威的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不要忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪!雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事,渡,你看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.20,0:07:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为飞弹的爆炸炸开了雪\N我才见到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?原来雪你从这爆炸中\N保护了这幼苗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪好伟大!\N真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.64,0:07:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么严寒的地方\N竟也可生长真是顽强呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.38,0:07:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢,就算第四界层\N变成了极寒地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.85,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雪底下也有生命\N努力求生存呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要加油呢,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.64,0:07:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千人仙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.51,0:07:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你回来了吗?\N灼热之剑怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你看见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位观众,我来说明一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.95,0:08:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已知道了多恶达\N支配的创界山是有七层了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.56,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡现在身处的第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有座拿着\N灼热之剑的胡娜拉像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.49,0:08:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而第三界层便有\N拿着极寒之剑的亚撒姆像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.23,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为多把这两把剑\N交换了的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.83,0:08:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令这两个界层变得奇怪起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底渡能否把灼热之剑\N放回胡娜拉像身上呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险!回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?你们是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是多恶达大人\N手下的四天王其中三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔界残兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.88,0:09:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟要我们出手\N你也干得有点儿不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是有点儿中的有点儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你们称赞\N我一点也不高兴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种口气也只有到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你\N把灼热之剑放回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止我便阻止我试试吧\N来吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.05,0:09:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点用也没有,受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,没事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪,西蒙,谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了!你怎么办?渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以啊,师傅,古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.95,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛武一郎流,交叉字斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.18,0:11:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单,简单\N二哥,是时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真卑鄙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.96,0:12:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战神丸!振作点!\N起来,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我杀了你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.24,0:12:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,合体吧!\N古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.76,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.81,0:12:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小儿科,豹,恶鸟\N合体变成合体达吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…很巨型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是大便有用的\N说得对,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.60,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,去吧,天空龙牙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.68,0:13:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙牙拳没有效,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.15,0:13:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打中!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,不能动,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?渡\N到此为止了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.10,0:13:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没,炎龙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙雷拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今次到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞龙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.10,0:14:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他接住了登龙剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.52,0:14:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登龙剑,破解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!登龙剑啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死期终于到了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!奋斗!\N你输了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.38,0:14:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡在冰雪下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会输吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.88,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在冰冷的雪下\N支配着的草苗还有其他生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.05,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可以输的\N我一定会令这个世界复原的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.72,0:14:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好\N那么我也要战斗到底!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!渡,这是火炎登龙剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.71,0:15:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,去吧,火炎登龙剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.98,0:15:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.28,0:15:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用理我\N快点把灼热之剑放回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.83,0:15:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.36,0:16:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要回来\N快把灼热之剑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.77,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.60,0:16:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,只差一步真是可惜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.96,0:16:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你慢慢地长睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.34,0:16:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.94,0:16:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灼热之剑,请你救渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.08,0:17:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐,你记着啊,渡\N不会就这样算数的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.79,0:17:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事?\N我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.80,0:17:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡娜拉和亚撒姆救了你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.03,0:17:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,快把灼热之剑放回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于连第四界层的彩虹\N也恢复原状了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好\N一定是很辛苦的旅程了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.50,0:18:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平时提起精神啊,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.93,0:18:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,最后的时刻到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的时刻?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.10,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去叫火龙把力量传给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.87,0:19:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你便可以复原了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命已燃烧尽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.94,0:19:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.60,0:19:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的\N因为还剩下三个界层啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.60,0:19:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能…不能一起去\N我不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.06,0:19:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有很多同伴,合力战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.61,0:19:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.84,0:19:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸…龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸变成一个球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.89,0:19:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N龙神丸死了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会这样的,今后怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟会发生这种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.60,0:20:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.49,0:20:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.69,0:20:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡! 渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.40,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你把灼热之剑还回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多谢你\N花朵和动物们也很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.37,0:20:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡娜拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了答谢你\N告诉你一个好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.17,0:20:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第五界层听说有复活圣水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活圣水?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.50,0:20:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了正义而牺牲了性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.38,0:20:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说可以利用圣水\N从死者之国回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.16,0:20:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带变成了龙之王的龙神丸\N上第五界层吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到第五界层的哪处?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.63,0:21:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找西里露森林吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西里露森林…\N谢谢你,胡娜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.61,0:21:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上第五界层\N我祈求能找到复活圣水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.91,0:21:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.02,0:21:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你拿勇者之剑出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者之剑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.83,0:21:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.60,0:21:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把勇者之剑加入了\N极寒之剑和灼热之剑的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.94,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增强了成为王者之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王者之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直战斗到这里的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.98,0:21:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以好好运用的\N你拿去吧


